extends layoutBS

block content
    .body
      .margin
        h2.text-monospace Potato
          .margin2
        hr
        br
        h3.text-monospace.font-weight-bold Hotels
        br
        .jumbotron
          form.text-monospace(method="post")
            .form-row
              .form-group.col-md-4
                label Destination
                input.text-monospace.form-control(name="destination" type="text" placeholder="e.g. Boston")
              .form-group.col-md-4
                label Visitors
                input.text-monospace.form-control(name="visitor" type="number" placeholder="e.g. 2")
              .form-group.col-md-4
                label Date
                input.text-monospace.form-control(name="date" type="date" placeholder="06.10.2018")
            .form-row
              .form-group.col-md-6
                label Brand
                select#hotel(name="brand").form-control
                  option(selected="") Choose...
                  option Hilton
                  option Sheraton
                  option Westin
                  option Four Seasons
                  option Ritz-Carlton
                  option Hyatt
                  option Renaissance
                  option Embassy Suites
                  option InterContinental
                  option JetBlue
                  option Hyatt Regency
                  option Shangri-La
                  option Wyndham
                  option Grant Hyatt
                  option Fairmont
                  option JW Marriot
                  option Sofitel
                  option Loews
                  option Mandarin Oriental
                  option Conrad
                  option Peninsula
              .form-group.col-md-6
                label Travel Purpose 
                input.form-control(name="purpose" type="text" placeholder="e.g. business")
            .form-row
              .form-group.col-md-6
                label Service 
                select.text-monospace(name="service").form-control
                  option(selected="") Choose...
                  option Free beakfast 
                  option Pool
                  option Family Friendly
                  option Great View
                  option Quiet Area 
                  option Gym
              .form-group.col-md-6
                label Star
                select(name="star").form-control
                  option(selected="") Choose...
                  option 5+ stars 
                  option 5 stars
                  option 4 stars
                  option 3 stars
                  option 2 stars
                  option 1 star
            button.btn.btn-warning.btn-lg.text-center(type="submit") Go
        br
        hr
        h5.font-weight-bold.text-monospace Best Hotels 
        .row
          .col-4
            #list-tab.list-group.text-monospace(role="tablist")
              a#list-home-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action.active(data-toggle="list" href="#list-1" role="tab" aria-controls="home") Nihi Sumba Island, Indonesia
              a#list-profile-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-2" role="tab" aria-controls="profile") The Brando, Tetiatoa, French Polynesia
              a#list-messages-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-3" role="tab" aria-controls="messages") Lodge&Spa at Brush Creek Ranch, Saratoga, Wyoming
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-4" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") Lodge at Kauri Cliffs, Matauri Bay, New Zealand
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") Gibb's Farm, Karatu, Tanzania
              a#list-settings-list.list-group-item.list-group-item-action(data-toggle="list" href="#list-5" role="tab" aria-controls="settings") More
          .col-8
            #nav-tabContent.tab-content.text-monospace
              #list-1.tab-pane.fade.show.active(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-home-list")
                |A cluster of rustic-luxe villas perched above a stretch of unspoilt Sumbanese coast, Nihi Sumba hotel feels perched on the edge of the world.
                |Preserved from urban development, this off-the-beaten-path Indonesian island is an idyllic setting for once-in-a-lifetime romance.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/nihi.jpg' width='60%')
              #list-2.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-profile-list")
                |The Brando is a unique luxury resort on French Polynesia’s breathtakingly beautiful private island of Tetiaroa – an atoll composed of a dozen small islands surrounding a sparkling lagoon 30 miles northeast of Tahiti.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/brando.jpg' width='60%')
              #list-3.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-messages-list")
                |The Lodge & Spa at Brush Creek Ranch, a luxury boutique guest ranch in Saratoga, Wyoming, is the perfect place to unwind and experience life on true working ranch in the Great American West.
                |From log-hewn buildings to stone fireplaces to plenty of outdoor activities, this Saratoga guest ranch makes every guest feel at home on 30,000 private acres.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/lodgebrush.png' width='50%')
              #list-4.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                |With sweeping views of the Pacific Ocean, The Lodge at Kauri Cliffs hotel on the North Island of New Zealand entices at every turn.
                |A four hour drive from Auckland, this hideaway is set in the middle of 6,000 acres near Matauri Bay – overlooking Cape Brett and the Cavalli Islands.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/kauricliff.jpg' width='50%')
              #list-5.tab-pane.fade(role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-settings-list")
                |Gibbs farm is not just a stop off point for the Ngorongoro Crater and other nearby safari delights.  It’s a hotel that offers peace, tranquillity and a return to a different way of life!
                |The guests are actively encouraged to become at one with their surroundings and emerge themselves into the ‘rhythm of the farm’.
                br
                br
                img.card-img-topimg(src='/images/gibbsfarm.jpg' width='50%')
        br
        br
        br
        hr
        h3.text-monospace.font-weight-bold Top Reviews
        .row
          .col-10
          .col-2
            a.text-warning.text-monospace(href="/hotelReviews") Write a review             
        form.text-monospace(method="post" )
          ol
            each review in hotelReviews
              .jumbotron
                i #{review.name} - (#{review.hotelName}) - #{review.city}, #{review.state}
                .row
                  .col-4
                    b #{review.reviewTitle}
                  .col-2
                    b Rating: #{review.rating}
                  .col-5
                    i #{review.hotelName}
                e Travel Purpose: #{review.purpose}
                br
                e Reviews: #{review.review}
                br
                e Photo: #{review.photo}
                br
                b Other info:
                br
                e Service: #{review.service} Location: #{review.location} 
                br
                e Food: #{review.food} Value: #{review.value} 
                br
                e Cleanienss: #{review.cleanienss} Entertainment: #{review.entertainment} 
                br
                br
